\id JAS - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG James 01 18/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h DIAęž‰MESI
\toc1 Diaęž‰mesimaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\toc2 Diaęž‰mesi
\toc3 Diaęž‰mesi
\mt1 Diaęž‰mesimaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Kodaęž‰ make Tekehali Yesu Ketiso yaaponaęž‰ e pokaaso hali halome. Do wape pitolo ekitaęž‰ hande ikaęž‰ kenke nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemeke Isulai 12 tapake ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasome. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome.
\s1 Hone tulaasaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hone epeke u tiaasaęž‰eki yaapo
\p 
\v 2 Ya kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ la handaęž‰laęž‰eki taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 3 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaleme ekinaęž‰ la handaęž‰laęž‰eki epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki takaęž‰lawaluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 4 Kutupa takaęž‰lapa pua haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰siki na minaęž‰paęž‰lake otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone halimikie.
\p 
\v 5 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ epeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki yonkaęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipao hataęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao halo halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ halieke.
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ haliepatetaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ hone ti na yokeke hone tulao hataęž‰ honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke. Hali epimaęž‰ hone ti yokeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo pomaęž‰ dawala ikali ho aęž‰meiyao lopatiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 7-8 Kutu piki halitaęž‰ hone ti yokolo hataęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±la na hake Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ honke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yelieke.
\s1 Natehali hasaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hamoko hasaęž‰eki yaapo
\p 
\v 9 Mo natehali kamemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki mea aęž‰meiyaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 10 Kutupa make mo hamoko kamemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki mininiaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo hande ambu palapalamanu paeyo halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ paelieke laa loaęž‰me.
\v 11 Oli natemaęž‰taęž‰ titipu wopu pitolo hataęž‰ opaęž‰liao yopulu hataęž‰ hande ambumanu hapuao halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo palapala manunaęž‰ kiliki lia ta wilie ekitaęž‰ dutu pa pa pu lopaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoeyaalieke. Koto tupaęž‰ mo hamoko halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bisinisi pitolo hataęž‰ homilieke.
\s1 La handaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hone pulaęž‰eki yaapo
\p 
\v 12 Hali epimaęž‰ mo la handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu epenaęž‰ kone daĚ±oĚ±la hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilieke. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo la handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao bepolaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yenki halolo hataęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki kone halieke. Koto yenkitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki halueke laa pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰me.
\v 13 Hali epimaęž‰ mo la handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ipulu haenaęž‰ hoke hone mea u tiaasaęž‰eki taapunaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do tupaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do hoke hone mea u tiaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epenaęž‰ la piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Hoke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone u tiaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke hone u tiaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 14 Mo halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone honaęž‰maasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hoke hone u tiaasaęž‰me.
\v 15 Pa wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ weki pitao mendiaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ hande ipikaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰eki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo weki daetaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki daeyatia puaataęž‰ hande some otaęž‰ homaalieke.
\p 
\v 16 Otaęž‰ ya kametitio. Yayapikieki na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 17 Mo epeke tupaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao make mo epeke alemanu kitaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao make oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Hande ya nane haleme paĚ±aĚ± piki ale manunaęž‰ Ateke paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao ipulu hataęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki topo na pealieke. Kutupa paa laęž‰kaęž‰leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tu na pilieke.
\v 18 Ipikaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hamonoyeke ipikaęž‰ hande otaęž‰ pi manunaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pitolo hataęž‰ niki mea hamono laęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Opua piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 19 Otaęž‰ ya kametitio. Do pimanu hone wipe. Iki paeyao pi opuluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa pi pi aĚ±iĚ± na leke make mineke aĚ±iĚ± na pankaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do alo pi manutaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.
\v 20 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mineke pankeleme ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tikitikipiki haumanu na peaasememe.
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ keke loluekemaęž‰ hoke hone witaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu paeyao make daeyatia pulu hataęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao make otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ neke mea daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ pi alemanu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ nokaęž‰paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ mea mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 22 Hande pi ale manutaęž‰ pa katakemaęž‰ homeke opitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone makeaasememe. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ pi opuataęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 23 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Hande pi alemanu pa opua kone na pitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo suĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ leke popeleke handaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 24 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke handaęž‰laęž‰pate laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ handeaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kutaa kone hone yonkaęž‰laotaęž‰ hone paa nimina wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 25 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ mo hande seliapopiki pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu hande wandaęž‰hali kaęž‰laęž‰pao halaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ kotoeki manunaęž‰ hando haotaęž‰ pa katakemaęž‰ homeke na opiki opua otaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ pitolo haenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaalieke.
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso halie la alaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ kekeke na handeteke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone makeao hao ipikaęž‰ Ketiso halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki diaęž‰me paekie.
\v 27 Hoe maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki otaęž‰ Ketiso tikitiki hautaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dupae alaęž‰me. Pa haleme weki wandiki make kineke wandaęž‰sunu make ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki handaataęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make mo kenke haumaęž‰ na hoeyaenaęž‰ alomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ alaęž‰me.
\c 2
\s1 Paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandake aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau walaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1 Ya kametitio. Hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ honditi na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 2 Hamoko hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ kolo lini pitao dau epekeeki pambaaso hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotieleme paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa hoke dau pambao natehali hali make epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 3 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo epeke dau pambaalaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Neke do sea seliaponaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitie laataęž‰ Kutupa mo hande natehali hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Neketaęž‰ pa tiao hae o IĚ± pilu sea anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pukunaęž‰ pitie laa lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 4 kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapotaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea telipaaso hataęž‰ honditi na pilimipe. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tumiki haliweki mea haaso hataęž‰ hoke hone wilimikie.
\p 
\v 5 Ya kametitio. Opuaęž‰pe. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki natehali wandaęž‰halio laa alemepatetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali talopu meataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ iki hamoko mea yaasaęž‰me. Kutupa make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lelieke.
\v 6 Kutu piliepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hande natehali wandaęž‰hali yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaememe. Mandane haliweki epi amedamaęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homao halemepe o pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ iki yolaęž‰ mea pu halemepe. Hande hamoko haliwekimaęž‰ koto hau pu haleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto haliwekimaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ biki epeketaęž‰ pa hoke biki laa hoeyao halememe.
\p 
\v 8 Nikaęž‰ you halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰peke alaęž‰ pi opua pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pilimikie.
\v 9 Kutu pilimipatetaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kototaęž‰ hoke hau pilimikie. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pi manunaęž‰ ulaęž‰eki yambilimikie.
\v 10 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande Lo Pi manunaęž‰ homeke kone yambeleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kototaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu paeyaonaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pilieke.
\v 11 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu na tunkulaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰pate doeki make Homenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na liaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu make na tunkuluaęž‰maęž‰ alepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ lili ekinaęž‰ mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao yambeleme.
\v 12 Wandaęž‰hali kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaasaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ koto pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pilimiki laa hone witolo hataęž‰ pi pi la peaęž‰tiki peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 13 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki na pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepe mo hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ teke halimaęž‰ mo hau pilie hali paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ na homilieke. Kutu piliepate mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ panisi pealo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ bepolalieke.
\s1 Hone tulao hataęž‰ piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 14 Ya kametitio. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halome alaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hau na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipape. Koto tupaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 15 O nakaęž‰ anaęž‰ kame dau ne diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ pa pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 16 kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ Keiyae. Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ loke titipu pinaęž‰ dau yama ne make naa da polenaęž‰e lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu na haleke pa pi homeke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epeke ekitaęž‰ ekipa pilipikipe.
\v 17 Hande Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halome alaęž‰ halitaęž‰ dupae. Pa pimaęž‰ homeke laa otaęž‰ hau pitolo hataęž‰ na leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paeki pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 18 Kutu piliepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ dupa lelieke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone tulao hale ekinaęž‰ hone witelepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ya hau pitolo ekinaęž‰ hone witolome laa lelieke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lolueke. Yaka hau pitolo ekimaęž‰ ya hone tulaalo ekitaęž‰ waluepate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hau na piki nakaęž‰ hone tulao hale ekitaęž‰ ekipa walipikipe laa lolueke.
\v 19 Nakaęž‰ hone tulale ekitaęž‰ dupae. Kodaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰me ale ekitaęž‰ epeke alepate pa mo hande hoke temoko manumaęž‰ make koto lo halemepatetaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ lo halememe.
\v 20 Neketaęž‰ hone na wiki halio. Hande otaęž‰ hau na piki pa pimaęž‰ homeke Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halome alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paeki pitaęž‰laęž‰me la walonope.
\v 21 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hayeke teke hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ekipa tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ leekepe. Hande ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Aisaęž‰ke mo oloda manda wia Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia haluekemaęž‰ pieke ekimaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 22 Ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyekeeki make ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau piekeeki make homeke hau paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone na witelepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyeke ekitaęž‰ peneme yaeyekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa make mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ leekeeki make otaęž‰ yaeyekeme. Hande leekeeki dupa
\q1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\m Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Neketaęž‰ yaka yankekee laa leekeme.
\m 
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halemeeki homeke na handeke ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitelemeeki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ handataęž‰ tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilipikie.
\p 
\v 25 Hande hali yolo hayeke wandaęž‰ Leihaęž‰pemaęž‰ make dupiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande Diosuamaęž‰ tapaeyeke iya ikiki haliweki handaęž‰ mea potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa tapaeyekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa temoko na pilaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hali toko ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau na piki hone tulaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hali tokomaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 3
\s1 Kekeke handeteke hapaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Ya kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ haliweki wopu walaęž‰laęž‰ hali haluekemaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo pa wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki pilie tupaęž‰ na piki pa mo disa haliweki nikinaęž‰ hau wotu handilieke.
\v 2 Niki paeyaomaęž‰ hoto elekeeleke hao hoeyaęž‰tiki pitolomaęž‰pate hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki hali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone puki paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ loke make anaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke hatiki pilieke.
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande hosi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ mo ayeni ale hapulao niki pi opinaęž‰ alomaęž‰me. Kutupa nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ nane poluekemaęž‰ make hande maęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mea pulumaęž‰me.
\v 4 Mo hande sisima paęž‰taęž‰ make hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ale tieke kone po tiekemaęž‰ mea puaasaęž‰patetaęž‰ mo hande kapidini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ nane poluekemaęž‰ mo hande mendeke nane hapulaalaęž‰ alesiki laęž‰kaęž‰lolo hataęž‰ kone potaęž‰ mea puaasaęž‰me.
\v 5 Koto tupaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hande kekeke make hosiki alesikimaęž‰ kone pi tieke lomono lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa hande ti ulekesiki paęž‰taęž‰ make hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ti polu tieke kone mo ti uleke sikimaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ tapaalieke.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa kekeke make ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ honemanu u tiaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa loke paeyao hoeyao halaęž‰me. Kutupa loke paęž‰taęž‰ ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hando halaęž‰me. Kutupa nikaęž‰ potaęž‰ pominolomaęž‰eki make yanko halaęž‰me. Dupiki ti talaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ ipu halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 7 Do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yeti paeyao make keto delikaęž‰ make batiti paeyao make dawala ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make haliwekimaęž‰ homu peaapeke yolo hataęž‰ ambaęž‰ homu pealemepate
\v 8 kenke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kekeke homeketaęž‰ homu peaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo hande kekeketaęž‰ lu mininiapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰eki yolo hataęž‰ hoke ale pitaęž‰ hali homaasaęž‰ ekimanu tumba pilaęž‰eki yaalo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homao halaęž‰me.
\v 9 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kekekemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lo halomaęž‰pate hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰yeke wepia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kone hoke pimanu lo halomaęž‰me.
\v 10 Keiyae pi alomaęž‰eki make hoke pi alomaęž‰eki make homeke kake paęž‰taęž‰ kone ipu halaęž‰me. Ya kametitio. Do ekitaęž‰ na pumanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo.
\v 11 Hande ikali opaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ manutaęž‰ tende pikieki make teto pikieki pitaęž‰ apaęž‰tao na ipu halaęž‰me.
\v 12 Ya kametitio. Nose timaęž‰ make olipi kiliki na aęž‰ilieke. Kutupa pumaęž‰ make nose kiliki na aęž‰ilieke. Koto tupaęž‰ damena ikali pilaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ epeke ikali meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Oli ya nanemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ hone epeke u tiaasaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 13 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali epi amedamaęž‰ hone wopu wia pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu hando halemepe. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeke halaęž‰eki peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ hone wopu wia homu pea hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hau pu halieke.
\v 14 Kutu piliepate honditi wotu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make pasaęž‰tei hau puluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰laęž‰eki make ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi ikaęž‰ kone na laake yayapiki hau na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 15 Dupiki hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hepeni naneeki diaęž‰me. Kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kenke lokenaęž‰eki make hoke temokonaęž‰eki make kotoeki tepomaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 16 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Honditi pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hapeke na yaalo hataęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao ipu halaęž‰me.
\v 17 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ hone epekeeki dupae. Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la kipabaake hone witaęž‰laęž‰ekie. Kutupa make puki lopaęž‰niao pilaęž‰eki make yopu halaęž‰eki make homu pea halaęž‰eki make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolo hataęž‰ epeke haumanu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make paeyao ya nanemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰patetaęž‰ honditi pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make yayapiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make apaęž‰tao na ipulaęž‰me.
\v 18 Mo hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaaseme haliwekimaęž‰ nokaęž‰peleme wae alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki opilieke.
\c 4
\s1 Do kenke haunaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki ipulaęž‰eki make ape alaęž‰eki ipulaęž‰eki make koto haumanu ipulaęž‰eki teketaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ ekimanu ikaęž‰ loke tukiki nane kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ leke ale liaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ peaasaęž‰me.
\v 2 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yolo hataęž‰ hali luekemaęž‰ taapeleme. Kutupa make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ meawee laa honemaęž‰ pitelemepatetaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yolo hataęž‰ ape la aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitelememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ honke na alemeke handa na minelememe.
\v 3 Kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ honke alemeeki make anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ hone u hoeyaaso hataęž‰ honke aleme ekinaęž‰ na minelememe.
\v 4 Ikitaęž‰ pi tunkuleleme wandaęž‰halio. Do ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Hali epimaęž‰ do kenke hau puluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali halaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ make hali epimaęž‰ do kenke haunaęž‰ yankeke haluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali haluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 5 Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paekie hone witelemepe dupae. Hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki loke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaalaęž‰ temokomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ wotu taapilieke wape paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 6 Kutu piliepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wopue. Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki doe.
\q1 Hakoko liteleme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia halaęž‰pate
\q1 homupiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki pa halo halaęž‰me wape paęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ Sadani paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Sadanitaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pelieke.
\v 8 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki make iki teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halieke. Hoke hau peleme wandaęž‰halio ikaęž‰ kiki tandaęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke. Hone yaapo wilimi wandaęž‰halio hone hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea bao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 9 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eĚ± lapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ kitalemeeki topo pea eĚ± lapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki make topo pea kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 10 Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki mea aęž‰meiyalieke.
\s1 Yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau peleme pi aĚ±iĚ± na lapaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Ya kametitio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone witolo hataęž‰ la la pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi na lapaęž‰peke. Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone witolo hataęž‰ pi lao pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ handa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ na pitaęž‰laęž‰pate mo hande Lo pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu hone na wiki neketaęž‰ mo Lo Pi manunaęž‰ pi yokaalu pitele hali halipikie.
\v 12 Mo hande Lo pimanu ulaęž‰ Hali Kodaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ kone pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰eki make hoeyaasaęž‰eki make anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laake hautaęž‰ neketaęž‰ aleke paęž‰taęž‰ hone wia hataęž‰ alepe. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi yokaalu piki hautaęž‰ neketaęž‰ aleke paęž‰taęž‰ hone wia hataęž‰ pitelepe.
\s1 Hakoko liaamaęž‰naęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu
\p 
\v 13 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ doeki lo halememe. Amepe o beliape daoni teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ bapi homekemanu tupaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ bisinisi pitolo hataęž‰ yenki wotu mulumeke la alemepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ doeki alome.
\v 14 Belia aęž‰ndaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ iki hone na wilimime. Ikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipape. Ikaęž‰ haleme ekitaęž‰ mo hande koa aęž‰pa pamba hosiki hao kilaęž‰pa pulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ halememe.
\v 15-16 Dupa lapaęž‰peke alee. Tekehalimaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ niki daęž‰ta hataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ doeki peataęž‰ moeki pulumeke la lapaęž‰peke alee alopate ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hakoko litolo hataęž‰ pi wotu hapaęž‰leleme. Kutu piki pi hapaęž‰leleme ekitaęž‰ hokeekie.
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ tikitiki hau peaęž‰pekeeki hone wia hataęž‰ kone otaęž‰ na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 5
\s1 Hamoko wandaęž‰hali kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1 Hamoko wandaęž‰halio. Do pi opuaęž‰pe. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ piki ekimanu epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ eĚ± lo hapaęž‰peke.
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ alemanu ambaęž‰ kukutu paęž‰laęž‰me kutupa make ikaęž‰ dau manutaęž‰ hoke hoke alesunumaęž‰ naakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ wialaęž‰me.
\v 3 Ikaęž‰ kolo silipa ale manunaęž‰ makaęž‰taęž‰ ikiki ambaęž‰ talaęž‰me. Kutupa koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hokeeki peneme yaalieke. Kutupa ikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handilieke. Kutupa mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamoko alemanu ambaęž‰ amu pealememe.
\v 4 Opuaęž‰pe. Ikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliwekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ makeaaso hataęž‰ mandaneeki na haleke pa wia haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ pi alaęž‰me. Kutupa make ikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliwekinaęž‰ pi alemeeki make oli ya nane halaęž‰ ami haliwekinaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 5 Ikitaęž‰ nate paeyao kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ epeke epeke alemanu minolo hataęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa ne wopu no halememe. Kutupu halemepate ikaęž‰ imeke wopu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki liaęž‰peke nate ipulaęž‰me.
\v 6 Mo handeeki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitaęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pi yokaalu pea lilimime.
\s1 Homu pea handeteke hataęž‰ yeni piaęž‰pekeeki
\p 
\v 7 Ya kametitio. Tekehali epenaęž‰yeke handeteke hao hapaęž‰peke. Mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ halaęž‰ alemanu napeke epeke tupaęž‰ winaęž‰yeke handeteke halaęž‰eki handelememe. Lako panakeeki make wetepenaęž‰eki make handeteke halaęž‰me.
\v 8 Kutupa iki make handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate koto kone yaęž‰leke handa ikaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 9 Kametitio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu peaapaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi la alualu na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Opuaęž‰pe. Hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ hali Kodaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ kone aęž‰pa halaęž‰me.
\v 10 Kametitio. Hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pimiki ekitaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ tanda pikieki minolo hataęž‰ kone puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa haemekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa mo hande puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki ambaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰me lo halomaęž‰eki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hande Tekehalimaęž‰ honkopu hao handeteke hayekeeki make mo paelo pieke dinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki epeaeyekeeki make ambaęž‰ opuelememe. Tekehalimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make hone wopu witaęž‰laęž‰eki make ambaęž‰ handelememe.
\s1 Dutu Otaęž‰ Tekehali alaęž‰ pinaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 12 Ya kametitio. Pi tieke doe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeninaęž‰ biki make do kenkenaęž‰ biki make alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ biki make na laęž‰ wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa Aowe loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ pa Aowe pi homeke lapaęž‰peke. Kutupa make Diaęž‰me loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ pa Diaęž‰me pi homeke lapaęž‰peke. Tekehalimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pilieke la loaęž‰me.
\s1 Tikitiki piki halinaęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 13 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ yeni pinaęž‰e. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laaso hataęž‰ emelimanu lenaęž‰e.
\v 14 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ yeni haasaęž‰pe. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande siosi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ handeteke haleme tondiki haliweki wi laęž‰ mepi peataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ biki laa oetamaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ yankaotaęž‰ ipiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaotaęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.
\v 15 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ mo hali wamo pitolo hataęž‰ mea tialieke. Kutupa mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaalieke.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ yeni tandela haluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu kaęž‰laęž‰pa alualu peataęž‰ kutupa ikaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Tikitiki yao halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ yeni piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wele wotu pilieke.
\v 17 Hande Elaidiataęž‰ nikimaęž‰ handeke hali kone hayekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lako na epenaęž‰yeke honkopu hao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piekepate bapi teponaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ lako na epeekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa koto hoki nane yeni pa piekepate ya nanemaęž‰ lako epeeketaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ ne pa anaęž‰naęž‰ wiekeme.
\s1 Lopaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 19 Ya kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande otaęž‰ pimanu yonkaęž‰lao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa hali homekemaęž‰ mo hali laęž‰kaęž‰la pa hatuku epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 20 Hali epimaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ some maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hokeeki yonkaęž‰lao epenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ some na homeke mea daęž‰taenaęž‰ lataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao make pa paeyaenaęž‰ lelieke. 
